  <Notes>
    <Note Caller="1" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References/>
      <Content>There may be some slight difference of meaning between ἐρωτάω[a] and ἐπερωτάω[a], but this cannot be determined from existing contexts.</Content>
    </Note>
    <Note Caller="2" LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="" LastEditedBy="">
      <References/>
      <Content>ἐπερωτάω[b] may be somewhat more intensive in meaning than ἐρωτάω[b], but both seem to be somewhat weaker in urgency than αἰτέω and παραιτέομαι[a] ({D:33.163}).</Content>
    </Note>
